{"tid":41651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[三性家奴]英國開綠燈 明年批准三親嬰兒療法","createTime":"2016-12-16T05:13:09.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-16T07:59:32.000Z","uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eedda754578957a74003935dc4a23d35e7df767a","tid":41651,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:13:09.000Z","msg":"英國政府周四正式開綠燈，准許有基因變異的父母，在人工受孕時加入第3者的脫氧核糖核酸（DNA），以防止嬰兒遺傳疾病，是全球首個國家准許該項備受爭議的治療。估計首宗治療將于明年春天展開。<br />\n<br />\n英國人類生殖與胚胎管制局主席切希爾周四宣布，容許診所及醫院申請使用線粒體基因療法（MRT），稱這是歷史性的決定。MRT會將第3者的DNA加至試管嬰兒，以消除缺陷線粒體導致的不治之症，嬰兒因而會擁有3名&ldquo;父母&rdquo;的基因。<br />\n<br />\n這項生育技術是由英國紐卡斯爾大學的科學家倡導，科學家指現時已有女性輪候治療，希望可在一年內治療25名女士。<br />\n<br />\n英國國會今年2月表決通過，准許取自3個人的DNA製作試管嬰兒，但醫院在引進這項治療法前，需經人工授精暨胚胎管理局批准。每個病人必須分別考量，由人工授精暨胚胎管理局核發同意使用此療法的許可。"},{"pid":"78531fc947e318a52e96ada806440d7bb6086692","tid":41651,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:20:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dfa319b2f85d3ff7d1f4caf0617420af3a98cfb","tid":41651,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:37:01.000Z","msg":"即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e3d2cf0b3e79f3f26f749f9f758352eb10312f3","tid":41651,"uid":2416,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:41:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>即係點<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n改DNA黎醫遺傳性疾病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d5eec3be33da51656cff251923ea91b1702332d","tid":41651,"uid":27030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T05:46:28.000Z","msg":"開乜撚野綠燈呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"507147c297e3e4a9ad5e9b2db3e11ef6b67e9aa4","tid":41651,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-16T07:59:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開乜撚野綠燈呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n開綠燈都唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}